Note: Base Function Creation Helpers
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "create_variadic_numeric_function" that takes nothing returns RFunction:
    Note: Create c() function signature

    Let param be a value of type RParameter with
        name as "...",
        type as create_any_type,
        has_default as false,
        default_value as null,
        is_variadic as true

    Return a value of type RFunction with
        name as "c",
        parameters as a list containing param,
        return_type as create_numeric_type,
        is_generic as false,
        is_s3_method as false,
        is_s4_method as false,
        package as "base"
End Process

Process called "create_single_param_int_function" that takes nothing returns RFunction:
    Note: Create length() function signature

    Let param be a value of type RParameter with
        name as "x",
        type as create_any_type,
        has_default as false,
        default_value as null,
        is_variadic as false

    Return a value of type RFunction with
        name as "length",
        parameters as a list containing param,
        return_type as create_integer_type,
        is_generic as false,
        is_s3_method as false,
        is_s4_method as false,
        package as "base"
End Process

